  "description": "This individual is a human woman of early middle years, with brown eyes set beneath a straight brow that gives her face a settled, appraising cast. Brown hair is kept in a practical, close-tied arrangement, exposing a broad cheek line and a jaw strengthened by habitual clenching. Taupe skin bears the ingrained staining and faint old nicks common to hands long accustomed to glasswork and the handling of casks. Her build is compact and durable, with forearms and shoulders developed through repetitive bar labor rather than formal soldiery.",
